
# 🏊 Crystal Pools Sales Analysis System

This project is a beginner-to-intermediate Excel sales analysis and commission tracking system created using Microsoft Excel.

The spreadsheet simulates a real-world business sales environment where pool-related products are sold across different locations, and employee commissions and profits are calculated automatically using Excel formulas and business logic.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Project Overview

The project analyzes sales transactions for a company called “Crystal Pools” and includes:

• Product sales tracking
• Profit calculation
• Employee commission analysis
• Sales location tracking
• Product-wise transaction records
• Pivot table summaries
• Business reporting and analytics

The spreadsheet contains transaction-level sales data along with a summary analysis sheet using Pivot Tables.

