Excel Shortcuts Used

Ctrl + C → Copy
Ctrl + V → Paste
Ctrl + Z → Undo
Ctrl + S → Save Workbook
Ctrl + D → Fill Down
Ctrl + R → Fill Right
Alt + = → AutoSum
F2 → Edit Selected Cell
Ctrl + Arrow Keys → Fast Navigation
Ctrl + Shift + L → Apply Filters
Ctrl + T → Convert Range to Table

